name: ferrous-metal-processing-plants-new-york-state-shapefile-1998
notes: This data set includes ferrous metal processing plants in the United States. The data represent commodities covered by the Minerals Information Team (MIT) of the U.S. Geological Survey, and the companies are those considered active in 1997 and surveyed by the MIT.
